{"tid":1562391,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"島崎遙香近況曝！燒肉店打工惹粉心疼","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T09:26:06.000Z","uid":253829,"like":72,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"e3e5d12495aec28837d295d775b2e67c1d95c4c7","tid":1562391,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:54:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/11/2123966-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2F2123966-XXL.jpg&h=8f99d26b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者孫伊萱／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的日本女星島崎遙香長相甜美，曾是日本女子天團AKB48的人氣成員， 當時以她擔任Center領軍演唱的畢業單曲，更是首週就賣出超過118萬張，不過在2016年畢業，離開AKB48後，工作量銳減的她，雖然有想要積極往影視界發展，接拍電影和電視劇，但在裡面都只是飾演配角，人氣急速下滑。近日更被拍到在燒肉店打工，令人不勝唏噓。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/11/2123964-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2F2123964-XXL.jpg&h=63a24cf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n島崎遙香近年來不斷突破自我，嘗試了不少角色，去年還在深夜劇《Repeat~改變命運的10個月~》中，獻出螢幕初吻，又大搞SM，還在米倉涼子主演的《LEGAL V～前律師小鳥遊翔子～》扮演了一名在東京高級夜店兼職的陪酒女。之前在受訪時，島崎遙香也曾說過：「想要繼續往演員之路邁進。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/11/2123963-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2F2123963-XXL.jpg&h=173aa57b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但似乎觀眾對於島崎遙香的演技非常不買單，人氣大不如前的她，日前也被網友發現在一家燒肉店兼職打工，幫客人點餐和送餐，影片在網路上被瘋傳，引起網友一陣譁然，大家都懷疑是不是她的生計是不是真的出了問題了，不然為什麼現在身為一名女演員的她，還要這樣在外抛頭露面。此外，該燒肉店的老闆還是她昔日隊友內田真由美所經營，據悉，不少AKB前成員在離隊後，都有去那邊打過工。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/09/11/2123965-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F09%2F11%2F2123965-XXL.jpg&h=f807009b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d9e0527000696df95994859289efb5ad08ad59c","tid":1562391,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"3bd9cdf73f8262318e26c0869eda94f873ba9408","tid":1562391,"uid":29080,"like":32,"dislike":32,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:01:56.000Z","msg":"好似麻友咁做雞咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f947edc83f5869f759c1db6899b0a4ee218ed3","tid":1562391,"uid":166474,"like":56,"dislike":14,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:04:22.000Z","msg":"拍AV啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8faf3c1e920cc5faefd35b208f91e401548d1c3","tid":1562391,"uid":45498,"like":12,"dislike":4,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"3bd9cdf73f8262318e26c0869eda94f873ba9408","tid":1562391,"uid":29080,"like":32,"dislike":32,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:01:56.000Z","msg":"好似麻友咁做雞咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:07:20.000Z","msg":"點解麻友係雞"},{"pid":"c10377bb10e271ae01a996261324a425ee488717","tid":1562391,"uid":244723,"like":237,"dislike":0,"score":237,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T04:09:21.000Z","msg":"一個明星做正常人既工作就心疼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nOn99"},{"pid":"aa5635d05ce0e97c